quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig, by the olive"
  95,2,By Mount Sinai
  95,3,By the yonder secure city
  95,4,Assuredly We have created man in goodliest mould
  95,5,Thereafter We cause him to return to the lowest of the low
  95,6,Save those who believe and work righteous Works. Theirs shall be hire unending
  95,7,What hencefort shall make thee belie the Requital
  95,8,Is not Allah the Greatest of the rulers